org.made.neohabitat

Interface Constants

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    HabitatVerbs
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Avatar, Bag, Box, Container, Flashlight, Ground, HabitatMod, Head, Key, Knick_knack, Magical, Massive, Openable, Region, Rock, Short_sign, Sign, Switch, Table, Tree, Walkable, Wall

    public interface Constants
    The PL1 Habitat application was monolithic and depended heavily on symbolic constants throughout. These are implement here as public static final values, but keep their original names. Every Habitat Mod has access to these "global constants" through the HabitatMod abstract superclass.
    Author:
    randy
